OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1784814496
OL,3,CThree arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cattempted murder after suspected knife
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FThree people have been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of attempted murder
OL,9,Ffollowing a disturbance in Newcastle
OL,10,Fcity centre, Northumbria Police have
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FOfficers have told us they received a
OL,14,Freport just after midnight, in the
OL,15,Fearly hours of Monday (20 July), that
OL,16,Ffour people had been involved in an
OL,17,Faltercation in the Blackett Street and
OL,18,FJohn Dobson Street areas.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
