FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1784814496
OL,3,CThree arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cattempted murder after suspected knife
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FEmergency services attended and a 20-
OL,8,Fyear-old man and two boys, aged 17 and
OL,9,F16, were taken to hospital with what
OL,10,Fpolice described as "serious injuries
OL,11,Fconsistent with having been caused by
OL,12,Fa bladed article".
OL,14,FAll three remain in hospital, their
OL,15,Finjuries are not believed to be life-
OL,16,Fthreatening.
OL,18,FThe 20-year-old man, a different 17-
OL,19,Fyear-old boy and the 16-year-old boy
OL,20,Fhave been arrested on suspicion of
OL,21,Fattempted murder.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
