PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1784814496
OL,3,CThree arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cattempted murder after suspected knife
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FNorthumbria Police has launched an
OL,8,Finvestigation, a number of cordons
OL,9,Fwere put in place but these have now
OL,10,Fbeen removed.
OL,12,FOfficers believe that all those
OL,13,Finvolved are known to one another.
OL,15,FAnyone with information is being urged
OL,16,Fto contact Northumbria Police via the
OL,17,Fforce website or by calling 101.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/3
